### ğŸ“˜ Overview  
**QuickKart** is a full-stack e-commerce web application developed as part of my **CloudThat Azure & DevOps Capstone Project**.  
The project demonstrates the use of **Microsoft Azure services**, **DevOps automation**, **security best practices**, and **monitoring** for real-world cloud deployment.

---

## ğŸ§± Project Architecture  

| Component | Technology | Azure Service |
|------------|-------------|---------------|
| Frontend | Angular 13 | Azure Static Web App |
| Backend API | .NET Core 3.1 | Azure App Service |
| Database | SQL Server | Azure SQL Database |
| Images | Azure Blob Storage | Blob Lifecycle Policies |
| Login Service | Azure Function (C#) | Function App (Serverless) |
| Monitoring | Application Insights / Azure Monitor | Alerts, Logs & Metrics |
| Security | Azure Key Vault | Secret Management |
| CI/CD | Azure DevOps Pipelines | Build + Release Automation |

